  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You make a simple push with your Vectors. Make a melee ninjutsu attack against a target within range, pushing it 30 feet and knocking it prone on a hit. A target that collides with a solid object has their movement stopped, and takes falling damage equal to the distance they could not move.</p><p>If you use this jutsu against a creature you have <strong>lifted</strong>, one attack automatically hits and doubles the distance that target is pushed, and the condition then ends.</p><p><strong>At Higher Ranks</strong>: For each rank you cast this jutsu above D-Rank, increase the cost of this jutsu by 3 and the number of attacks by 1.</p>",
